descriptionHTML:
This amazing watch face is specially designed for those, who got used to wearing elegant and stylish watches.
Watch Faces by YSAR design are absolute symbols of style. Watch faces by YSAR Design are compatible with both round and square android wear smartwatches: Moto 360, Asus ZenWatch, LG G Watch R, LG G Watch, LG Watch Urbane, Samsung Gear Live, Sony Smartwatch 3 etc..

Custom features:
- Battery indicator
- Date
- Analog 2nd time zone watch
- Advanced and luxury design with superb readability
- Ambient mode

If you have android wear and want to add something special and beautiful to your smartwatch, then watch faces by YSAR Design are for you. Our watch faces are elegant and modern at the same time. Be special with YSAR Design.

Our watch faces are available in settings right after you download from store and are simple in being set up. YSAR watch faces do not require much electric energy, so your smartwatch will operate for almost the same period of time as usual.

Check out our watch faces with different features and designs: https://play.google.com/store/apps/developer?id=YSAR+Design.
We have analog and digital watch faces, watch faces with skulls and slumber mode. We are trying to match any taste by introducing different watches of all styles bcbgmaxazria.

Please, rate, share and write comments, because we want to improve our watch faces and satisfy your needs.
